Class Student

Object
User
Student
public class Student extends User
The Student class represents a Student user in the system, inheriting from the User class. It includes methods for viewing open camps, registering for camps, submitting enquiries, and more.
Author:
Felicia Poh, Tey Cia Meng, Gao Linyue

  • Method Details

    • openCamps

      public void openCamps()
      Updates the camps available to the student to list of open camps. Checks for previously registered camps, and blacklists students that have withdrawn from the camp before. Checks for faculty camps. Checks visibility of other faculty camps that are open to the whole of NTU.
